  <brief_title>Combination Vaccination Before HIV Treatment Interruption</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study to Determine the Impact of Therapeutic HIV Vaccination Followed by a Scheduled Interruption of Antiretroviral Therapy on HIV-Specific Immune Function and Virologic Rebound in Patients With Prolonged Viral Suppression</official_title>
